title: Activating LV 'Pve/Data' Failed:   Check of Pool Pve/Data Failed (Status:64). Manual Repair Required!
tags: _fix proxmox
roam-id: 1994ae19-9b52-49f4-9392-81022eea3eb4
type: text/markdown

- this happens when your virtual machines on proxmox occupy more storage than the lvm-thin has to offer

- open up your proxmox shell and issue

  ``` shell
  lvconvert --repair pve/data
  ```
